Description: DigitalHydraulic LLC exists to assist customers in reaching their objectives by providing technology that allows supreme efficiency.
Headquarters Regions: Great Lakes, Midwestern US
Full Description: DigitalHydraulic LLC exists to assist customers in reaching their objectives by providing technology that allows supreme efficiency and system flexibility. The Company seeks to become the company recognized for creating and introducing the technology that transformed not only the hydraulics industry, but hydraulics, itself, into the fastest and most efficient form of power transmission. In a breakthrough insight in 2001, Elton Bishop invented the Digital Hydraulic Transformer (DHT). Using a unique and simple linear reciprocating mechanism, the DHT is a paradigm shift from conventional rotary hydraulic transformer designs to convert hydraulic power from one flow and pressure to another flow and pressure. Simply put, the DHT allows cyclic use and re-use of hydraulic, potential and kinetic energies in manner that approaches proverbial "perpetual energy". As an example of the extreme efficiency the DHT allows, the retrofit of a prototype DHT into the hydraulic system of a forklift allowed over 70% reduction in the amount of prime mover energy required to complete standard workcycles. It is anticipated that, with further development, the DHT will allow energy savings of over 90%.

Description: Midwest New Beginnings Incorporated (M.N.B.I.) is an Omaha, Nebraska based company that has a primary focus of addiction.
Headquarters Regions: Midwestern US
Full Description: Midwest New Beginnings Incorporated (M.N.B.I.) is an Omaha, Nebraska based company that has a primary focus of addiction based rehabilitation for individuals in need of an inpatient and outpatient form clinical help. M.N.B.I. provides an alternative approach to addiction rehabilitation, and does not take the traditional 12-step route like other programs found across the country. It is common that in rehabilitation programs participants are encouraged and sometimes even required to attend some form addiction anonymous meetings either daily or weekly. M.N.B.I. will take participants to these meetings if they wish to incorporate anonymous meetings into their program, but participants will be doing so with out any outside force swaying them in one direction or the other. M.N.B.I. utilizes a rehabilitation program design that has shown very promising results that have lead people to lead future lives where they are free of addiction, and then capable of moving on with their lives in the pursuit of happiness. M.N.B.I.'s mission can be broken down into three goals that are obtainable, but they require continuous work in order to consider each goal as accomplished. These three goals are: a) put Omaha, Nebraska on the map as one of the leading places in the country to attend when entering an addiction rehabilitation inpatient treatment program, b) show the world that not every rehabilitation needs to be a 12-step program, and c) give their participants a new start with life, addiction free, allowing them the possibilities to right their wrongs, and spend the rest of their days as happy as possible.

Description: Oshiboree, Inc. provides a fashionable after-market carrying case for baby wipes, in 3 sizes to accommodate different size wipes.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Oshiboree, Inc. provides a fashionable after-market carrying case for baby wipes, in 3 sizes to accommodate different size wipes. The full size would be convenient for purses, desk drawers, and glove compartments.  The ""slim"" or medium size would be for flushables/toddler/feminine wipes. This would replace the current trend of carrying these in plastic baggies.  And the smallest would be sold as a component piece to any cosmetic company that sells their own brand of facial/make-up remover wipes as a gift with purchase. This case is brandable with the in-mold design offering the ability to have corporate or personal logos and designs.    The word ""Oshibori"" is the term for ""moist towel"" in Japanese and refers to that lovely hot or cold towel one gets at the beginning of a meal.  To be able to have that convenience anytime, anywhere is what Oshiboree provides.  What makes Oshiboree different is that the case is not only beautiful, but it provides a seal to keep the wipes from drying out.  Because the artwork on the case is extremely customizable, the potential for designer prints and limited editions helps to maintain the high-end accessory nature of this product.  Baby wipes are not just used by moms and babies.  Most car owners like to have them handy.  Germ awareness is increasing in our country and abroad.  The potential for outlets includes not only boutiques and baby stores, but automotive stores, car washes, high-end retailers, department stores, and big box stores like Target.

Full Description: Protect a site with AuthPilot API, a two-step authentication that helps users to access a website using their phone number. This extra step is valuable because it adds security to blogs and websites with sensitive information. In the RESTful API, the site features the endpoints of create a user, update a user, text a user and call a user. Packagist and Github are two sources where developers can find additional documentation if they prefer to use the PHP API.
